      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116936117464567647</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 15:52:30 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;📬 Trunk &amp;amp; Tidbits for June 2026 is now live!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our monthly blog post series is there to showcase what we worked on last month.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this edition, we are also discussing our official Helm Chart for Mastodon, for those of you who deploy Mastodon on Kubernetes. We released a brand new version of the chart in a new place, deprecating the existing one.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://blog.joinmastodon.org/2026/07/trunk-tidbits-june-2026/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;blog.joinmastodon.org/2026/07/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;trunk-tidbits-june-2026/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/mastodev" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;mastodev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/mastoadmin" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;mastoadmin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/TrunkAndTidbits" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;TrunkAndTidbits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <category>mastodev</category>
      <category>mastoadmin</category>
      <category>trunkandtidbits</category>
    </item>
    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116856425277313070</guid>
      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116856425277313070</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 14:05:43 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We just released Mastodon 4.6.3, containing several bug fixes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Full release notes and update instructions are available on the GitHub release page.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/mastodon/mastodon/releases/v4.6.3" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;github.com/mastodon/mastodon/r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;eleases/v4.6.3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/MastoAdmin" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MastoAdmin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <category>mastoadmin</category>
    </item>
    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116810207094278507</guid>
      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116810207094278507</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 10:11:50 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We just released Mastodon 4.6.2, 4.5.13 and 4.4.20. Those versions only update our container image to fix an important security issue in ffmpeg, which Mastodon uses to process videos.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you do not use our container image, you may skip this update but you need to update your installed ffmpeg to a patched version (ffmpeg 8.1.2, 7.1.5, 6.1.6, or 5.1.10)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Full release notes and update instructions are available on the GitHub release page.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/mastodon/mastodon/releases" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;github.com/mastodon/mastodon/r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;eleases&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/mastoadmin" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;mastoadmin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <category>mastoadmin</category>
    </item>
    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116806085498460059</guid>
      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116806085498460059</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 16:43:39 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We just released Mastodon 4.6.1. It contains several important bug fixes and we recommend every instance running 4.6.0 to update.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are also releasing Mastodon v4.5.12 and v4.4.19 with small bugfixes and a fix to a critical security issue affecting servers using LDAP_TLS_NO_VERIFY=true.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Full release notes and update instructions are available on the GitHub releases page.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/mastodon/mastodon/releases" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;github.com/mastodon/mastodon/r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;eleases&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/mastoadmin" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;mastoadmin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <category>mastoadmin</category>
    </item>
    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116754951213266902</guid>
      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116754951213266902</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 15:59:32 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The second release candidate for &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/Mastodon" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Mastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 4.6 is now out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It addresses several issues found in 4.6.0-rc.1, and is expected to become 4.6.0 later this week.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can see all the changes on the release page: &lt;a href="https://github.com/mastodon/mastodon/releases/tag/v4.6.0-rc.2" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;github.com/mastodon/mastodon/r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;eleases/tag/v4.6.0-rc.2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you are an admin, updating ahead of the full 4.6.0 release would be a great help to find and squash any last-minute bugs!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/MastoAdmin" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MastoAdmin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <category>mastodon</category>
      <category>mastoadmin</category>
    </item>
    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116736365625682506</guid>
      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116736365625682506</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 09:12:59 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;For &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/Mastodon" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Mastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; app developers and fellow &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/fediverse" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;fediverse&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; platform developers, with the approaching Mastodon 4.6 release we&amp;#39;ve put together an overview of new and changed APIs that you may want to look at! Collections, profile editing, &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/Wrapstodon" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Wrapstodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and more:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://blog.joinmastodon.org/2026/06/mastodon-4-6-for-devs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;blog.joinmastodon.org/2026/06/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;mastodon-4-6-for-devs/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <category>mastodon</category>
      <category>fediverse</category>
      <category>wrapstodon</category>
    </item>
    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116736348998401511</guid>
      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116736348998401511</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 09:08:45 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Following last week&amp;#39;s beta, the first release candidate for &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/Mastodon" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Mastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 4.6 is out! 🎉 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can find all of the changes on the release page: &lt;a href="https://github.com/mastodon/mastodon/releases/tag/v4.6.0-rc.1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;github.com/mastodon/mastodon/r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;eleases/tag/v4.6.0-rc.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We aim to publish the release next week. If you are an admin, now is a good time to upgrade to the release candidate and help us find any last minute bugs!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/MastoAdmin" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MastoAdmin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <category>mastodon</category>
      <category>mastoadmin</category>
    </item>
    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116687020382482250</guid>
      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116687020382482250</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 16:03:50 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We will soon be publishing a blog post for Mastodon client developers, showcasing the new API and features that are available in this version.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/mastodev" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;mastodev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/mastodonapi" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;mastodonapi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <category>mastodonapi</category>
      <category>mastodev</category>
    </item>
    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116687014689391748</guid>
      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116687014689391748</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 16:02:23 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We just released the first beta version of Mastodon 4.6 🎉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Highlights for this release are the profile page redesign and the ability to create curated Collections of Mastodon accounts, but it contains many other changes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can find all of them in the release page: &lt;a href="https://github.com/mastodon/mastodon/releases/tag/v4.6.0-beta.1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;github.com/mastodon/mastodon/r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;eleases/tag/v4.6.0-beta.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We aim to publish a release candidate next week. If you are an admin and want to be on the bleeding edge, now is a good time to upgrade to the beta version and help us find any last minute bugs!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/mastoadmin" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;mastoadmin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <category>mastoadmin</category>
    </item>
    <item>
