      <link>https://mastodon.social/@MastodonEngineering/116686417226647939</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 13:30:26 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We just released Mastodon 4.5.11 and 4.4.18.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;These versions contain a medium and a high severity security fixes as well as other bugfixes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Full release notes and update instructions are available on the GitHub releases page.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/mastodon/mastodon/releases" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;github.com/mastodon/mastodon/r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;eleases&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/MastoAdmin" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MastoAdmin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
