      <description>&lt;p&gt;We&amp;#39;re looking for two Backend Ruby on Rails Web Developers to work with us remotely as part of the core team.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ideally you are:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;1. Very experienced with Ruby on Rails&lt;br /&gt;2. Proficient in PostgreSQL, and familiar with Redis and Elasticsearch&lt;br /&gt;3. Experienced in developing maintainable and scalable web backend and API systems&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This remote full-time position requires a 4-hour overlap with the CET timezone.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For more info/to apply: &lt;a href="https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/mastodon/ac9d4f66-13e8-44d1-bb82-a929ebca8a27" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;jobs.ashbyhq.com/mastodon/ac9d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;4f66-13e8-44d1-bb82-a929ebca8a27&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/FediHire" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;FediHire&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/GetFediHired" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;GetFediHired&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/hiring" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;hiring&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/backend" class="mention hashtag" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;backend&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
